  <h1>About Me</h1>

  <p>
    I created this shop to help veterinary professionals stay organized, save time, and make clinic life feel a little less overwhelming.
    As someone passionate about veterinary medicine and efficient workflows, I know how busy things can be behind the scenes, from patient care and paperwork to keeping the whole day running smoothly.
  </p>

  <p>
    That is why I design clean, practical, and easy-to-use digital templates made specifically for vet clinics, vet techs, assistants, students, and pet care teams.
    Whether you are looking for printable forms, editable clinic templates, trackers, or workflow tools, my goal is to make your daily routine easier and more organized.
  </p>

  <p>
    Everything in my shop is made with care, simplicity, and real clinic life in mind.
  </p>

  <h2>Outside the clinic</h2>

  <p>
    When I am not designing templates, I spend time with my pets Juno, Luna, Sushi, and Sriracha.
    I also love reading, hiking, painting, and watching horror movies.
    Creativity and calm balance are a big part of my life, and they inspire everything I design.
  </p>

  <p>
    Thank you so much for supporting my small business, I am so happy you are here!
  </p>

